Muchidzidzo che[[taranyika]], '''chisipiti''' zvinoreva panzvimbo panobuda mvura ichitubuka yega kubva pasi. 

Panonaya mvura, imwe mvura inosinina ichipinda pasi pevhu. Yave pasi, mvura iyi inotevedza pane ivhu kana '''muwaridzwa''' wematombo ano[[bvinina]] (layer of permeable soil or rock). Mvura iyi inokwezvewa kuenda kunzvimbo dziri pakaderera kuburikidza ne[[gunganidzo]] re '''Earth'''. Nokuda kwegunganidzo, mvura yemuvhu inoda kuwungana ichigadzikana pasi ipapo kudzamara pamusoro payo pave muchechetere. Iwoyu muchechetere wemvura unodanwa kunzi [[tafura yemvura]] - ''water table kuEnglish''.

Imwe nguva '''muwaridzwa''' wematombo anobvinina unosvika paunobudikira paunosangana nepane [[nhika]] pauso hwenyika.  Ipapa kana [[tafura yemvura]] iri pakakwirira kudarika nhika iyi, mvura inotubuka kubuda mudombo ichizoonekwa sechisipiti.

Mune dzimwe nzvimbo mvura iyoyi inokwanisa kunge yayerera ichibatana nemuzera wedombo rinopisa zvokuti inotubuka panyika yave kudziya kuita chisipiti chinopisa  - ''Hot springs''.
